author: Disney
description:
Wishes come true in Disney’s timeless stories, and it doesn’t end there! As the world’s largest wish granter for Make-A-Wish, A Disney wish is granted every hour of every day. We are honored that wish kids choose us as their most heartfelt wish. 💖

Follow along during Disney’s Week of Wishes and learn how you can become a WishMaker for Make-A-Wish at wish.org/Disney. #DisneyWeekOfWishes
